          making the Confidential Information known to the public.
        </p>
        <h6>9.2 Remedies</h6>
        <p>
          Without prejudice to any other rights of the Corporation, the parties
          acknowledge and agree that if a Shareholder breaches or otherwise
          violates, or attempts to breach or otherwise violate, the provisions
          of this Article, the Corporation will likely suffer irreparable harm
          and an injunction or other like remedy shall be the only effective
