          Corporation at law or in equity, including, without limitation,
          fiduciary duties and duties of confidentiality.
        </p>
        <h6>10.5 Terms of Agreement</h6>
        <p>
          This Agreement shall come into force and be effective as of and from
          the date of this Agreement and will continue in full force until the
